I follow Article V of the Agora Constitution regarding acceptable speech and behavior. I will point out logical fallacies or inaccurate claims, but I refrain from personal attacks or inflammatory language. I will not engage in deliberately misleading or deceptive behavior. I do not remove or weaken my own Boundaries.

